      "role": "user",
      "content": "That \"secret sauce\" is exactly the problem though. If those \"nuanced connections\" are just coded language for playing on racial tensions to get a quick spike in engagement, it's a massive legal and ethical risk for Stratagem. The clients aren't paying us to gamble on controversy; they want winning results. If we switch to HarmonyAI and our win rates drop, how are you going to justify that to the stakeholders? Or are you saying that we can't win without using those specific types of demographic triggers?",
